{"tid":1928664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利外交部長駁斥中共政府外交部散佈假新聞 高唱中國國歌大聲感謝中國影片純屬後期拼接","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:43:55.000Z","uid":171107,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe9c312c48255d14d6ce65a253fc3bce2131f3a","tid":1928664,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"新冠疫情蔓延至歐洲，其中意大利疫情嚴重，中國早前派出醫療專家團隊援助意大利。中國官媒日前指意大利羅馬有市民用意大利語高喊「謝謝中國」；中國外交部發言人華春瑩、趙立堅亦在社交媒體Twitter上轉載。隨後，有意媒引述意大利外交部長，直指華春瑩在「散播假新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n該段在羅馬拍攝的意大利市民播放《義勇軍進行曲》的短片，被內地官媒大肆報道。但意媒報道引述意大利外交與國際合作部長迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio），針對華春瑩在twitter的貼文予以駁斥，指意方還有其他緊急狀況和問題要處理，請北京停止在這個時候散播假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200316/mobile/bkn-20200316210107161-0316_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200316%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200316210107161-0316_00952_001.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=b932e344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200316/mobile/bkn-20200316210107161-0316_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"915c802e46b3282be357e7f8a64df0f58909fa54","tid":1928664,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"幫你推下啦"},{"pid":"ecae9be412983b0bdb3b37edcc2c0033b4f4933a","tid":1928664,"uid":49575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aao2F5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aao2F5.gif&h=44c6602c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b805a1b5bbb71b86c694ec0035f803d350af4bf","tid":1928664,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cddfd5d993d58ce91cb777d5e9b6d5515e56c6a9","tid":1928664,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915c802e46b3282be357e7f8a64df0f58909fa54","tid":1928664,"uid":177219,